    <h1 data-i18n="title">‡∏¢‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö</h1>
    <p data-i18n="subtitle">‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏©‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏ß‡πá‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ</p>

    <div class="lang-row">
      <button class="lang-btn active" id="th-btn" data-lang="th">‡πÑ‡∏ó‡∏¢</button>
      <button class="lang-btn" id="en-btn" data-lang="en">English</button>
    </div>

    <button class="next-btn" id="next-btn" data-i18n="next">‡∏ñ‡∏±‡∏î‡πÑ‡∏õ</button>
  </div>

  <button class="back-btn" id="back" title="‡∏¢‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏±‡∏ö">
    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
      <path d="M15 18L9 12L15 6" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
